								"type": "wysiwyg_basic",
								"html": "<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t<div class=\"col\">\n\t\t\t<h6>JOIN THE BED &amp; BREAD CLUB TODAY</h6>\n\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\tWe are fully committed to meeting the direct needs of struggling families and individuals here in our community. But we can't help them without your support. By becoming a member of the Bed &amp; Bread Club, your monthly gift will make a real difference in the lives of the people we serve every day.\n\t\t\t</p>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"btgrid\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row row-1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col col-md-2 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"content\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://give.salvationarmycarolinas.org/give/439848/#!/donation/checkout?amount=other&amp;recurring=1&amp;utm_source=web&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_content=bedandbread500&amp;utm_campaign=smg&amp;c_src=22BBWIORGCSD22WSS&amp;c_src2=web\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"btn btn-solid btn-red\">$500</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col col-md-2 col-sm-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"content\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://give.salvationarmycarolinas.org/give/439848/#!/donation/checkout?amount=250&amp;recurring=1\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"btn btn-solid btn-red\">$250</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col col-md-2 col-sm-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"content\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://give.salvationarmycarolinas.org/give/439848/#!/donation/checkout?amount=other&amp;recurring=1&amp;utm_source=web&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_content=bedandbread100&amp;utm_campaign=smg&amp;c_src=22BBWIORGCSD22WSS&amp;c_src2=web\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"btn btn-solid btn-red\">$100</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col col-md-2 col-sm-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"content\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://give.salvationarmycarolinas.org/give/439848/#!/donation/checkout?amount=other&amp;recurring=1&amp;utm_source=web&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_content=bedandbread50&amp;utm_campaign=smg&amp;c_src=22BBWIORGCSD22WSS&amp;c_src2=web\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"btn btn-solid btn-red\">$50</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col col-md-2 col-sm-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"content\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://give.salvationarmycarolinas.org/give/439848/#!/donation/checkout?amount=other&amp;recurring=1&amp;utm_source=web&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_content=bedandbread25&amp;utm_campaign=smg&amp;c_src=22BBWIORGCSD22WSS&amp;c_src2=web\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"btn btn-solid btn-red\">$25</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<hr>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t\t\tThe inflation crisis has already caused countless families to stretch their dollars thinner and thinner. This year, low-income households are facing difficult choices.\n\t\t\t</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t\t\tPlease consider becoming a Bed &amp; Bread Club member today so we can continue to Do the Most Good for those in need, no matter the circumstances.\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>",
